'CPM commissions'=>'Comisioane CPM ',
'CPM (cost per mille) commissions are a special type of commissions that are rewarded for 1000 impressions, which means for displaying your banners 1000 times.<br/><a href="%s" target="_blank">More help in our Knowledge Base</a>'=>'"Comisioan CPM" (cost per mia de afisari) sunt un tip special de comisioane care sunt rasplatite pentru 1000 de impresii, ceea ce inseamna afisarea bannerului de 10000 de ori.<br/><a href="%s" target="_blank">Mai multe informatii in  Knowledge Base</a>',
'Forced matrix allows you to limit to the number of referrals of subaffiliates any affiliate can refer. It means that every affiliate can have only specified number of children. <a href="%s" target="_blank">More details read in our Knowledge Base</a>'=>'Matricea fortata permite limitarea numarului de referrals ai subafiliatilor la care orice afiliat se poate referi. Asta inseamna ca fiecare afiliat poate avea numai un numar specificat de "copii. <a href="%s" target="_blank">Pentru mai multe detalii citeste  Knowledge Base</a>',
'Hosting of %s on  %s servers.'=>'hosting-ul of %s pe  %s servere.',
'Multiple currencies allow you to track sales in multiple currencies.<br/><a href="%s" target="_blank">More help in our Knowledge Base</a>'=>'"Valute multiple" permite urmarirea vanzarilor in mai multe valute.<br/><a href="%s" target="_blank">Mai multe informatii in "Baza de cnostinte"</a>',
