'First row of graph represents how sale commission is divided between first affiliate, 
    last affiliate and other affiliates.'=>'Primul rand al graficului, reprezinta modalitatea de impartire a comisioanelor din vanzari intre primul afiliat, ultimul afiliat si ceilalti afiliati.',
'Second row represents which part of commissions is divided between all 
    affiliates and which part is directyly added to first and last affiliates.'=>'Al doilea rand reprezinta care parte din comision este impartita intre toti afiliatii si care parte este direct adaugata primului si ultimului afiliat.',
'You can see that commission for first(last) affiliate is not just first(last) click 
    bonus but also part of "commissions for others" is added to it.'=>'Puteti observa ca, comisionul pentru primu(ultimul) afiliat nu este doar primul(ultimul) bonus click dar la fel este adaugata si partea din "comision pentru altii"',
'If you want to change commissions rewarding you can set it in 
